      "actionDate": "2026-02-04",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Made in America Jobs Act of 2026</strong></p><p>This bill expands the criteria for various grants under the Economic Development Administration's public works program to include projects that facilitate the relocation of employment opportunities&nbsp;into the&nbsp;United States or the growth of the manufacturing sector.</p><p>Specifically, the bill modifies grants for (1) public works and economic development; (2) planning and administrative expenses; (3) training, research, and technical assistance; and (4)&nbsp;regions experiencing adverse economic changes.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-03-20T20:08:21Z",
      "versionCode": "00"
    }
